{"word":"ἐπισύρω","slug":"ἐπισύρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπισύρω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to drag</i> or <i>trail after</i> one, in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to crawl along</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to do</i> anything <i>in a slovenly way, to slur over</i>, <b><a href='S:Lysias'>Lys.</a></b>; <el>ἐπισύροντες</el> <i>confusedly</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>; often in <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>slovenly, careless</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}